name: Bright Lights, Big City (Debut EP)
description:
Purchase today the debut EP release from Beau and the Arrows. Featuring collaborations from the likes of American Vocalist Lauren McVan and upcoming rapper Cystal Dixon, this EP is a small taste into the sights and sounds of the group. 

Tracklisting:
1. Generation feat. Crystal Dixon
2. Fix
3. When I Die
4. Please Please Please! feat. Lauren McVan
5. Loaded Bliss
6. Depression
7. Alas
